## Supervised learning

This skill loads applicable corrections at skill-load time. Any rule
tagged with `{{SKILL_ID}}`, `general`, or matching this agent's role
({{ROLE_ID}}) injects into the prompt.

**Recording firings:** When a rule shapes a decision in this skill,
record it:

```python
from _framework.learning import record_firing
record_firing(rule_id="<id>", skill_tag="{{SKILL_ID}}", profile="{{PROFILE_ID}}",
              action_summary="how the rule shaped this run")
```

If a hard rule catches a violation attempt, set `was_overridden=True`
so the recapture detector and graduation gate see the breach.

## Action surface

