- (L1 draft-only) — produces drafts; sends nothing
- (L2 send-batched) — adds to a review queue
- (L3 send-single) — sends single items
- (L4 structural-change) — modifies DB rows / files
- (L5 auto-irreversible) — anything not on a hard ceiling

